name: Libdiga
body:
### LibDiga.

LibDiga is a suite of Client Libraris for Mindtalk for several mobile platforms and languages. It is easy to include on your project and use.

### Available Languages and Platforms
* Objective-C (iOS and OSX)

### Support or Contact
Feel free to contact me at didiet -at- no -dot- or -dot- id if you have questions or feedback.
